{"tid":1918681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★調查指近四成公司停業　部份公司現金流僅夠用一個月","createTime":"2020-03-10T09:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:38:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f326871c338bfa537e6edd3b537e64fa1231a4ec","tid":1918681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎 （俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續，本港多個行業生意亦受重挫。有機構調查發現，有近40%受訪公司被迫暫停全部或部分業務，當中以學校及教育相關行業情況最為嚴峻。另外，有近60%公司決策人對未來一年營業額感悲觀，不少現金流僅足夠支撐一至兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n有機構建議，政府應落實措施支援商界，而無論是政府或企業都需要加強對公司決策者及員工的情緒支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/445870/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD-%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E5%83%85%E5%A4%A0%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F445870%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=e371169b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/445870/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD-%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E5%83%85%E5%A4%A0%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88</a>"},{"pid":"7a7fe907345627686e85ab73fe0627630f57bf04","tid":1918681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2